name: @ag-grid-community/infinite-row-model
description: Advanced Data Grid / Data Table supporting Javascript / React / AngularJS / Web Components

scripts.insight-build: rimraf publish && npm run build && npm run package && npx gulp insightBuildOptimize && rimraf dist
scripts.insight-publish: rimraf tmp && git clone git@bitbucket.org:Projekt_EAGLE/build-ag-grid-infinite-row-model.git tmp && cd tmp && git rm -r * && copyfiles -u 2 ../publish/**/* . && git add --all && git commit -m "New Build" && git push origin master
scripts.build: npm run build-cjs && npm run build-es6

author: Sean Landsman <sean@thelandsmans.com>
